title: Plat 5 ADC main looking for duo
body:
Hi guys
Dynamic queue has been getting a bit depressing when going solo. One person makes a mistake and everyone's at each other's throats. Not as fun as a game should be.

I'm a plat 5 adc main looking for a duo to play ranked with. 
I (usually) only played 1-2 ranked games a day after 9pm, Brisbane time. 
Reply here or add me in game if interested!!

IGN: Soccersupastar
